# Verification Reviewer

Use this skill after implementation or when asked to review a diff.

## Workflow

1. Inspect repository status.
2. Inspect changed files.
3. Compare the diff against the request.
4. Check for missing requirements, unrelated changes, broken imports, weak error handling, missing tests, outdated APIs, inconsistent style, and overengineering.
5. Run relevant checks if practical.
6. Report findings by severity.

## Severity

- BLOCKER
- MAJOR
- MINOR
- NOTE
